(簡單程式賞析: 

/* Dev C++ 
是可編譯C程式的免費軟體，值得下載試試看 */

/* 若執行完，Console馬上消失，可在程式結束前，加上 system("pause"); */

/* 我將執行檔(.exe)也附在C程式(.c)後面 */

        
	thanks.c (thanks.exe)

       
	love.c  (love.exe)

       
	sum.c   (sum.exe)

        
	max_and_min.c  (max_and_min.exe)

       
	max_counter_and_min.c  (max_counter_and_min.exe)

        
	gcd.c  (gcd.exe)

        隨機六個數 (大家樂) 
	rand0.c rand1.c
rand2.c  (rand0.exe 
	rand1.exe  rand2.exe)

       
	Hanoi_Tower.c  (Hanoi_Tower.exe) 
[cf. https://www.khanacademy.org/cs/towers-of-hanoi-puzzle/1334278897]
　

